OL,3,CInside Makerfield: How Burnham defied
OL,4,Cthe polls in historic by-election
OL,6,FAndy Burnham won more than half of all
OL,7,Fvotes cast in the Makerfield by-
OL,8,Felection, comfortably beating the
OL,9,Fcombined total for second and third
OL,10,Fplace parties Reform UK and Restore
OL,11,FBritain.
OL,13,FThe now-former Greater Manchester
OL,14,Fmayor won 54.8% of the votes cast,
OL,15,Foutperforming all the opinion polls
OL,16,Fpublished during the campaign, none of
OL,17,Fwhich placed him above 50%.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
