OL,3,CInside Makerfield: How Burnham defied
OL,4,Cthe polls in historic by-election
OL,6,FMr Kenyon's 34.5% of the vote
OL,7,Frepresents Reform's second best
OL,8,Fperformance at a Westminster by-
OL,9,Felection to date, behind only the
OL,10,Fcontest in Runcorn and Helsby in 2025,
OL,11,Fwhere his party got 38.7%.
OL,13,FBoth Labour and Reform finished well
OL,14,Fahead of all other parties in
OL,15,FMakerfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
