OL,3,CInside Makerfield: How Burnham defied
OL,4,Cthe polls in historic by-election
OL,6,FMs Shepherd was the only other
OL,7,Fcandidate to get more than 5% of the
OL,8,Fvotes cast ` the threshold needed to
OL,9,Favoid losing the #500 deposit that all
OL,10,Fcandidates have to pay to stand for
OL,11,Felection to parliament in the UK.
OL,13,FThe Conservatives, Liberal Democrats
OL,14,Fand Greens, along with eight other
OL,15,Fcandidates, all got less than 5% of
OL,16,Fthe vote and lost their deposit.
OL,18,FConservative candidate Michael
OL,19,FWinstanley finished in fourth place
OL,20,Fwith just 2.2% of the vote.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
