OL,3,CInside Makerfield: How Burnham defied
OL,4,Cthe polls in historic by-election
OL,6,FThere were 15,696 votes cast for
OL,7,FReform, up 2.7% on the party's
OL,8,Fperformance in 2024; 3,111 for Restore
OL,9,F(which did not stand in 2024); 997 for
OL,10,Fthe Conservatives, down 8.7%, 308 for
OL,11,Fthe Greens, down 3.7%; and 163 for the
OL,12,FLiberal Democrats, down 6.4%.
OL,14,FThe other candidates got a combined
OL,15,Ftotal of 274 votes.
OL,17,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,18,Four political experts are across all
OL,19,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,20,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
